tting. Incorrect information could disqualify your application.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Step 3. Registration &#8211; Apply for the TCS BPS hiring process<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"729\" height=\"700\" src=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9200\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Scenario A: If you already have an account, log in and fill out the application form. After completing it, click on &#8216;Apply for Drive&#8217;.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Scenario B: If you&#8217;re new, click &#8216;Register Now&#8217;, choose &#8216;BPS&#8217; as the category, and fill in your details. Once completed, submit the form and click the  &#8216;Apply for Drive&#8217;.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Important: Ensure all details in the TCS Application Form are correct and complete, including academic information and any internships or work experience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Step 4:<\/strong> Choose &#8216;In-Centre&#8217; for the test mode, select your preferred test center and click &#8216;Apply&#8217;. Remember, once you&#8217;ve chosen a test center, you can&#8217;t change it later.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"982\" height=\"733\" src=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image-11.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9216\" style=\"width:740px;height:auto\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Step 5<\/strong>: After you&#8217;ve applied, go to &#8216;Track Your Application&#8217; to confirm your status. You should see &#8216;Applied for Drive&#8217; as your status. This tells you that your application has been submitted successfully.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"976\" height=\"571\" src=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image-15.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9221\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you don&#8217;t see &#8216;Applied for Drive&#8217; as your status, this indicates your application might not have gone through. You might need to check if you missed any steps or if there were errors in your application.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If everything is correct and you still don&#8217;t see the status, you might need to wait more. Sometimes it takes time for the status to update. Once your status shows &#8216;Applied for Drive&#8217;. This means your application is in the system and you&#8217;re registered for the drive.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, you have to wait for further communication from TCS. They will let you know about any next steps or instructions. Candidates must track their application status to ensure everything is progressing smoothly. If you have any concerns or questions, contact  TCS support for assistance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s it! You&#8217;ve completed the application process for the TCS drive. Now, all that&#8217;s left is to prepare for the test and any interviews that may follow.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"documents-for-tcs-bps-application-form\"> Documents for TCS BPS Application form<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Candidates should submit all their original academic documents such as <\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li> Mark sheets<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Degree certificates<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li> Internship letters<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li> Work experience letters<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>  You&#8217;ll receive test-related communication from &#8216;TCS iON &#8211; Our Test Provider&#8217;. It&#8217;s important to keep your original academic documents ready for verification. TCS iON will send you all the information you need about the test, so be sure to check your emails regularly. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Make sure to have your documents in hand and keep an eye on your inbox for updates from TCS iON. This will help you prepare for the test without any hassle.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>TCS BPS Apply Online